        class="flex flex-col lg:max-w-56 gap-5 rounded-xl border-2 border-main-red shadow-gray-500 text-black bg-gradient-to-bl from-gray-200 to-gray-300 p-5"
      >
        <h4 class="font-semibold text-xl text-center">
          Flight Program Application
        </h4>
        <p>
          If you are interested in enrolling in one of our flight programs,
          please download and fill out this application. You may bring it in to
          our office or email it to us at <a
            href="mailto:eperalta@flyredarrow.com"
